| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-3669 — Recovery Inhibition (qilin)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 2b99d956-f68f-5dd8-a52e-3bbc479dc3a1"
